content: Sorry, you don't have access to this section

comment.text: This key displays a message informing the user they lack permission to view a specific section. It appears within a "No Access" container, likely in a visual area like an empty state or restricted area of the UI, and is used for both Room and Account access restrictions. Translators should ensure the tone is polite and informative.
